@node "Future" "Plans for the future"
@{fg highlight}THE FUTURE DEPENDS ON YOU...@{fg text}


@{i}Version 4@{ui} (coming soon!)

  - no more screens but @{b}pages@{ub}, which can also be displayed
    on the workbench!


@{i}Version 5@{ui} will probably support new elements on the menu screen:

  - fields for string input
  - file-lists
  - a new textview program
  - the abiltity to use every font within the MMEditor program. 


@{i}Version 7@{ui}:

  - 45 billion color mode
  - real time execution
  - built-in 76 bit fractal generator
  - MS-Windows (TM) compatibility
  - Commodore (will they still exist?) VC 1541 disk drive support
  - Airbag
@endnode

